            { type: "Challenge", text: "Puppet Master. For 5 mins, you cannot speak. You can only communicate by nodding. The person to your right answers for you." },
            { type: "Truth", text: "Do you prefer to be dominant, submissive, or a switch? Why?" },
            { type: "Dare", text: "Allow a partner to use a belt or scarf to lightly bind your wrists together for one round." },
